title: Shoplyfter - Aften Opal NEW 17 October 2018
description: October 17th, 3:27 pm, Case # 0851993 - Young, white adolescent teen suspected of theft violently resists apprehension by loss prevention officer. Loss prevention officer is forced to tie suspects wrists to chair in order to ensure safety. Suspect is informed that she has been caught on camera stealing an elder customers purse. Suspect initially denies claims as further interrogation techniques are deployed. The rest of this case file is considered classified.
